data.description: Searching for a Lake Home?  This Home is perfect for full time living or a Second home at the Lake.    This well kept home is in the Woodhaven Shores Development where people come to enjoy the lake.  Just a short walk to High Rock Lake where the water just calls to you for fishing, swimming and having fun.  There is a voluntary HOA that provides a boat ramp, dock and a picnic area for only $80 per year.   Sit on the front deck and enjoy life or head down to the water, this property offers it all.  All appliances convey!! More Pictures to be added tomorrow!
